name: Iron Bank Enhanced Compound Finance Lending
description: Supplies {{token}} to [Compound](https://app.compound.finance) and opens a long-term debt on [Iron Bank](https://docs.cream.finance/iron-bank/iron-bank) for an additional amount of {{token}} to earn COMP. Earned tokens are harvested, sold for more {{token}} which is deposited back into the strategy.
